		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />It is not hard when you know how to do it, when you already have an experience. If you just a newcomer, it is hard, actually - you need to figure out that you need header, you need to find docs on it, you need to write correct header without being sure you doing it right. So either autogeneration of header or just provided ready-made template with header could help greatly at starting point.

		

