	</tr>
	<tr>
		<td colspan="2"><hr class="sep" />You can force NESASM to use ZP access when needed.
<br />
<br />lda $00 is actually lda $0000, but lda &lt;$00 is ZP.

		

		</td>
	</tr>
	</table>


